Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.07,0:00:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於賀家小女兒的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.14,0:00:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想到他們一族全都投靠黑團
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.58,0:00:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.38,0:00:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是不能理解賀家的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一族過去出過很多乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在之前的龍王戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也失去了好幾位親族
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安姊姊，我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一發生了\N讓凪大公啓動古風琴的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界會再度回到龍王戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，十二王戰爭之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點無論如何都得避兔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以老公王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請協助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長，妳變得相當出色了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們安南依照條約
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支援加爾德羅貝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公王，感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將彼此重疊的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖進記憶深處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟昨天不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我就站在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.23,0:01:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降臨而下的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:02:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔地包容一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.34,0:02:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我訴說著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「守護」的真正意義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾度仰望 無限寬闊的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘不了 那一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法再回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有失去什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量滿溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱切地 強烈地 勇猛地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在沒有光芒的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.37,0:02:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能感覺到聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有你能發現我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第22話 破滅之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多，不要急
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，請
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，他們走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓卡迪亞知道我們的恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭領…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，不對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入侵者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑谷的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是隸屬於阿爾泰公國陸軍\N近衛師團的謝爾蓋·王少校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有意思與諸位為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:04:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確保溫德布倫王國的真白女王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及其乙HiME\N愛莉卡·夢宮的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望各位儘快將兩位交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時限為正午
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點在「龍之墓場」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果遲到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之間的關係就不得不破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待諸位做出明智的選擇\N喂，妳這樣會被發現啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神部隊的信號過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始作戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自史密斯先生的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備的人醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，預備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能知道最後一段歌詞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追蹤隊在沙漠谷底發現垂死的她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最親近真白的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白，我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這絕對是陷阱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，還是得去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有耶，有耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像全國的乙HiME大集合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑰麗的縞瑪瑙也出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他們也有所覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次或許會有點棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算這樣我們還是得上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道是妳的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該把真白公主藏起來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判斷得好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在面對敵人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳至少得有這樣的警戒心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你是叔叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要援助我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是別找藉口了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被妳吸引了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也很意外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟妮娜一樣大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是承認
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被吸引了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被妳的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被妳總是看著前方追逐夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正直的眼神所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我違背殿下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算幫助妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次做出這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…結果卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是表面上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，這樣反而讓人看了難過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得清算一下\N自己做出來的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以阿爾泰軍人的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及妮娜父親的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:08:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我一定…也喜歡著…你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜她對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是理論而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…是我女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要以她父親的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做我現在做得到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我對妮娜的愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話，我希望妳投降
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追逐著夢想對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴獸？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白公主應該躲在不遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌學會了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀，我的運氣真是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下就只要試試看了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣，父…不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王少校的作戰就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不用這麼擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:10:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我交代過女武神們要緊盯住謝爾蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要她們絕對不可以沒監視到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果歌沒有錯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白和愛莉卡就沒有用處了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳希望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以讓她們完全下台
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把愛莉卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，她對妳來說很礙事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真是體貼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，妳的體貼只會產生痛苦喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳要使用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好久不見了，愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看妳這麼有精神，真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴，那身舞鬥服…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是凪大公給的Meister舞鬥服喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像靜留姊姊一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要人類主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加自由而優秀的舞鬥服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說愛莉卡啊，陪我跳支舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經興奮到胸口快裂開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為，我一直對妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厭惡到極點啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然可以跟Meister舞鬥服平分秋色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這力量真是了得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想從決定好的作戰行動逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會變成這樣的機關嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能看著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼至少得忍耐\N才能讓愛莉卡心無旁騖地戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命，怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非得知道不可嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古風琴…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是守護者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞鬥服…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是編織者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖籃曲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這段歌詞…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:12:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第一次聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第四段歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛…愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再抵抗了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連千繪學姊都…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負已分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，妳別在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們打算滅口的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該早就動手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個人共用一條命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有一方放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就結束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的蠢到棒極了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛突然這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且說聲來得好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是再打下去也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳打不贏我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這定論下太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愕天王！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要消除這股怨氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到星星的世界等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.26,0:15:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打敗了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亞啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡迪亞城…陷落了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是要歡迎我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有點做過頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，美也她是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，那個垃圾只負責執行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是我的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:15:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服那一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳池的事，還有健行考試也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳為什麼要這麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被靜留姊姊看上了\N讓我覺得很礙眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我希望妳消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後妨礙我的埃爾斯汀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她明明是個笨蛋\N就只是運氣好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過聽說她死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是自作自受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會做那麼愚蠢的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會得到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到姊姊…地位\N還有名譽等一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這乙HiME的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳以為埃爾斯…\N她是以怎樣的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯她…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真韌命，還能動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李梅，伸惠，貞德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧，英靈殿之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想殺死愛莉卡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那傢伙是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深…深優？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，我來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是之前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「詛咒的黑曜石」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受詛咒的女武神GEM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們為了生出這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而玩弄了蕾娜·賽雅斯的遺體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是那一位留下來的最優先指令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要解決掉你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區改造人的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.43,0:18:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能有多大能耐！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除4號到12號的拘束式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反物質裝置推力50%
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武具被…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優，不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，這玩意已經隨妳所欲了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，妳現在想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是傳說中的古風琴力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間轉移了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有地板耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這個了…這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我打算避開要害…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然起風暴？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.99,0:19:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「漆黑的金剛石」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親，你的傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮…妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳又…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，請退下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:21:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害我的父親的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不原諒！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍·瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高次物質化排序開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎小姐，請賜我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認艾莉莎·西爾斯的基因情報
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「月神 黃金劍」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其逃避 不如挺身面對更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是少女的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力唷\N就算內心突然感到寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.74,0:23:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以笑容面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼NO NO NO 你的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有快樂的未來 我想守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.92,0:23:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.13,0:23:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的心意 比寶石更耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.53,0:23:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.54,0:23:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這舞鬥服很棒吧\N（神秘山谷的愛莉卡）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會
